Game.....: Death Crimson OX
Origin...: USA - NTSC
Released.: August 9th, 200
Ripped.......: Nothing

July 29, 2010. The beautiful city of Saronica is destroyed by the mysterious SMO. Agents, known as Subliminers, are placed throughout the city to oppress the populace, but survivors form The Resistance and fiercely engage the SMO forces in battle. Lily, the elusive leader of this rebellion has been captured, and it's up to you as agent Kou Yanami to free her from their evil clutches. Armed with an ancient super weapon known as the Crimson you yield to no one, blowing away any SMO Subliminers who dare get in your way!